This paper deals with the design of optimal codes for MIMO MAC-DMT systems, which involves topics such as information theory, networking, signal processing, and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Signal Processing), cs.COMM (Communication), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
